

CNOOC International Ltd: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback
























cnooc international ltd
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Energy
Industry: Oil, Gas & Coal
Sub-Industry: Exploration & Production
CNOOC International Ltd. produces crude oil and natural gas. The Company engages in exploration, development, production, and sales of oil and natural gas. CNOOC International operates worldwide.




